    <item>
      <title>Tiktok面临超过5亿欧元的欧盟 - 中国数据出口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/tiktok-faces-fine-over-500-million-for-eu-data-sent-to-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Tiktok所有者Bytedance Ltd.将被非法将欧洲用户的数据运送到中国的隐私罚款超过5亿欧元（5.52亿美元）的隐私罚款，这增加了视频共享应用程序的全球强烈反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/tiktok-faces-fine-over-500-million-for-eu-data-sent-to-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 11:37:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克的总督支出斧头正在悬挂在技术库存上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/musk-s-doge-spending-axe-is-hanging-over-technology-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）努力削减1万亿美元的联邦支出为受虐的科技投资者增加了另一种风险，威胁要从已经不稳定的行业中获得数十亿美元的收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/musk-s-doge-spending-axe-is-hanging-over-technology-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 11:24:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Microsoft撤回了从芝加哥到雅加达的数据中心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/microsoft-pulls-back-on-data-centers-from-chicago-to-jakarta</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Microsoft Corp.已将全球数据中心项目撤回，这表明该公司正在更加努力地研究其为人工智能和云提供动力的服务器农场的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/microsoft-pulls-back-on-data-centers-from-chicago-to-jakarta</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 09:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税破坏植根于亚洲的比特币采矿供应链</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/tariffs-threaten-to-upend-bitcoin-mining-supply-chain-mara-riot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[劳伦·林（Lauren Lin）很着急。在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统启动关税之前，她只有不到48小时的时间从泰国到美国运送约5,600台比特币矿业机器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/tariffs-threaten-to-upend-bitcoin-mining-supply-chain-mara-riot</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 08:50:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果生产中心受到关税的打击，使股票暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/apple-shares-slide-after-tariffs-threaten-to-hit-production-hubs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司（Apple Inc.）在总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的新关税中直接发现自己，即使经过一年的努力使iPhone制造商免受贸易战和供应链中断的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/apple-shares-slide-after-tariffs-threaten-to-hit-production-hubs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 21:07:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
